Package game2D.objects

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackgroundObject
    Background objects are immovable objects of the game.
    BackgroundTile
    BackgroundTile are not added to BackgroundObject arraylist in GameWorld.
    BigExplosion
    BigExplosion plays when player dies
    Bullet
    Bullets are fired by player and enemy weapons
    Enemy
    Enemy objects in the game
    GameObject
    GameObject is the base class of objects in the game world.
    MoveableObject
    Moving objects in the game.
    PlayerShip
    PlayerShips are game players with input controls.
    PowerUp
    PowerUp holds an (upgraded) weapon to give to player.
    SmallExplosion
    Small explosions happen on bullet collisions with objects
